# Deployment @ Rinkeby

A sample relay contract has been deployed to the rinkeby testnet at [0x748abbafe7dc1fe107eecd49cb66046d468acb9b](https://rinkeby.etherscan.io/address/0x748abbafe7dc1fe107eecd49cb66046d468acb9b) with contract source code being verified.

Because the relay requires the improved idena node to generate the BLS public key with identity's private key(nodekey), this test case have to use random private keys to replace and simulate the identities of the real identities in idena blockchain now.

The test relay contract has been initialized with 2464 identities, and done one update operation which kills one identity.

Anyone can check the contract state [here](https://rinkeby.etherscan.io/address/0x748abbafe7dc1fe107eecd49cb66046d468acb9b#readContract), and can interact with this contract through [abi](https://rinkeby.etherscan.io/address/0x748abbafe7dc1fe107eecd49cb66046d468acb9b#code).
